The '''Corasgh''' were a sentient [[Species/Legends|species]] who, under the [[New Order/Legends|New Order]], established a nest colony located in the [[Koornacht Cluster/Legends|Koornacht Cluster]] of the [[Core Worlds/Legends|Core Worlds]]. This colony was wiped out when its planet was conquered in the [[Yevethan Purge]].

